        <abstract> 
<p>Sends a quotation from de Vallemont’s <hi rend="italic">Curiosities of nature and art in husbandry and gardening</hi> (1707) showing that the value of saltpetre in manure and the advantage of steeping seeds in specially prepared liquid manure were well known at the time.</p> 
